result.name: 生記粥店

reviews.text: The price is cheap and I think it is a very nice restaurant for light breakfast (congee) or even lunch (Chinese traditional fried noodle). I often visit this restaurant.
One of my favorite congee restaurants
Ok

I went there to try the fried dough(youtiao) and it was so so. I'd call it a bread, since it was very thick and soft. If you prefer that kinda youtiao you'll like it. I might go back to try their other menus, like their congee.

Just went early this morning due to recommendation.  The fried dough wrap 炸兩 is pretty oily and the minced beef is very heavy in salt.  I am very sensitive to these thing and am now developing that dry cough.  I would recommend other congee places in the surrounding streets.

result.adr_address: 香港新蒲崗錦榮街10號
result.name: 生記粥店

reviews.text: 這裡數月前，D食品還可以嘅！但數天前開始，D粥及腸粉；糉子， 都同數月以前不一樣，差！差！差！唉！又小一間幫襯！有錢，你方揾唔到美食？
佢啲啲嘢味道ok， 但係老闆娘啲態度真係麻麻， 十問九唔應， 慘過同佢乞米!  雖然在舖仔買嘢食， 唔係食禮貌， 但係都唔使咁差。  我寧願食轉角嗰間蘇記， 老字號， 不過賣咗鋪之後重開， 味道好得多， 而且有禮貌得多!
腸粉蘿蔔糕超好味
好食 抵食 開得早 方便街坊👍
$14碗艇仔粥，我敢話全香港最平最正，仲有好多款粥任揀縂有—/二款你啱食，蝦米腸$9，边度有咁平，雖然鼓油唔夠但有唔同醬料任落。好野
